 ``` 
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9044d-146">逗号字符用作同一行中单独 cookie 之间的分隔符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9044d-146">The comma character is used as a delimiter between separate cookies on the same line.</span></span>

  
  
